        (TUSNOM, TUSLONGUEUR
        ) VALUES
        ('DOMTRANSCO', 15
        ) ;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK TUSER DOMTRANSCO') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
BEGIN
    INSERT INTO LANTUSER VALUES
        ('DOMTRANSCO', 'FR', 'Domaine'
        ) ;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSER DOMTRANSCO FR') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
BEGIN
    INSERT INTO LANTUSER VALUES
        ('DOMTRANSCO', 'EN', 'Domain'
        ) ;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSER DOMTRANSCO EN') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
--REM INSERTING into TUSPARAM
DECLARE
    CURSOR C1
    IS
        SELECT DISTINCT DTRCODE FROM DATATRANSCODING;
    CURSOR C2
    IS
        SELECT DISTINCT LANCODE FROM LANGUE;
BEGIN
    FOR C1R IN C1
    LOOP
        BEGIN
            INSERT INTO TUSPARAM VALUES
                ('DOMTRANSCO', C1R.DTRCODE, NULL
                ) ;
            COMMIT;
            FOR C2R IN C2
            LOOP
                BEGIN
                    INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM VALUES
                        ('DOMTRANSCO', C1R.DTRCODE, C2R.LANCODE, C1R.DTRCODE, NULL
                        ) ;
                    COMMIT;
                EXCEPTION
                WHEN OTHERS THEN
                    ROLLBACK;
                END;
            END LOOP;
        EXCEPTION
        WHEN OTHERS THEN
            ROLLBACK;
        END;
    END LOOP;
END;
/
--CFS46474 END

    INSERT INTO LANTUSER
        (TUSNOM, LANCODE, TUSLIBELLE
        ) VALUES
        ('APJTYPE', 'EN', 'APJTYPE'
        ) ;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSER APJTYPE EN') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
BEGIN
    INSERT INTO LANTUSER
        (TUSNOM, LANCODE, TUSLIBELLE
        ) VALUES
        ('APJTYPE', 'FR', 'APJTYPE'
        ) ;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSER APJTYPE FR') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
DECLARE
    NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
    SELECT COUNT( *) INTO NCOUNT FROM TUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'APJTYPE';
    IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
        INSERT INTO TUSPARAM
            (TUSNOM, TUPCODE, TUPFLAGORFI
            ) VALUES
            ('DEFAULT', 'DUMMY', 0
            ) ;
    ELSIF NCOUNT != 0 THEN
        INSERT INTO TUSPARAM
            (TUSNOM, TUPCODE, TUPFLAGORFI
            ) VALUES
            ('APJTYPE', 'APJCODE', 1
            ) ;
    END IF;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK TUSPARAM APJTYPE TEST1') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
DECLARE
    NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
    SELECT COUNT( *) INTO NCOUNT FROM LANTUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'APJTYPE';
    IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
        INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM
            (TUSNOM, TUPCODE, LANCODE, TUPLIBELLE
            ) VALUES
            ('TEST', 'DUMMY', 'EN', 'DUMMY VALUE FOR EXTERNAL TABLE TEST'
            ) ;
    ELSIF NCOUNT != 0 THEN
        INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM
            (TUSNOM, TUPCODE, LANCODE, TUPLIBELLE
            ) VALUES
            ('APJTYPE', 'APJCODE', 'FR', 'TEST1'
            ) ;
    END IF;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSPARAM APJTYPE APJCODE EN') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
DECLARE
    NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
    SELECT COUNT( *) INTO NCOUNT FROM LANTUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'APJTYPE';
    IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
        INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM
            (TUSNOM, TUPCODE, LANCODE, TUPLIBELLE
            ) VALUES
            ('TEST', 'DUMMY', 'FR', 'DUMMY VALUE FOR EXTERNAL TABLE TEST'
            ) ;
    ELSIF NCOUNT != 0 THEN
        INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM
            (TUSNOM, TUPCODE, LANCODE, TUPLIBELLE
            ) VALUES
            ('APJTYPE', 'APJCODE', 'FR', 'TEST1'
            ) ;
    END IF;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSPARAM APJTYPE APJCODE FR') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;

    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK TUSER DFLTALLOCRS ') ;

        ) VALUES

        ) ;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSER DFLTALLOCRS EN') ;

    ROLLBACK;

/
BEGIN
    INSERT INTO LANTUSER
        (TUSNOM, LANCODE, TUSLIBELLE
        ) VALUES
        ('DFLTALLOCRS', 'FR', 'REASON '
        ) ;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSER DFLTALLOCRS FR ') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
DECLARE
    NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
    SELECT COUNT( *) INTO NCOUNT FROM TUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'DFLTALLOCRS';
    IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
        INSERT INTO TUSPARAM
            (TUSNOM, TUPCODE, TUPFLAGORFI
            ) VALUES
            ('DFLTALLOCRS', 'DUMMY ', 1
            ) ;
    END IF;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK TUSPARAM DFLTALLOCRS DUMMY ') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
DECLARE
    NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
    SELECT COUNT( *) INTO NCOUNT FROM LANTUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'DFLTALLOCRS';
    IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
        INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM
            (TUSNOM, TUPCODE, LANCODE, TUPLIBELLE
            ) VALUES
            ('DFLTALLOCRS', 'DUMMY', 'EN', 'DUMMY VALUE FOR EXTERNAL TABLE DFLTALLOCRS'
            ) ;
    END IF;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSPARAM DFLTALLOCRS EN') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
DECLARE
    NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
    SELECT COUNT( *) INTO NCOUNT FROM LANTUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'DFLTALLOCRS';
    IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
        INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM
            (TUSNOM, TUPCODE, LANCODE, TUPLIBELLE
            ) VALUES
            ('DFLTALLOCRS', 'DUMMY', 'FR', 'VALEUR PAR DEFAUT POUR LA TABLE EXTERNE DFLTALLOCRS'
            ) ;
    END IF;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSPARAM DFLTALLOCRS FR') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;

        LANTUSPARAM
        (
            TUSNOM
          , TUPCODE
          , LANCODE
          , TUPLIBELLE
          , TUPHELPTEXT
        )
        VALUES
        (
            'FRDINFLEAKTHRU'
          , '09'
          , 'EN'
          , '09 - FRDINFLEAKTHRU'
          , ''
        ) ;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LANTUSPARAM FRDINFLEAKTHRU 09 EN
') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;

        AND TUPCODE NOT LIKE('PCT%') ;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('OK LKTUPTACTPG PENALITE_RACHAT
') ;

WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;

--CASNT-1873 BEGIN
DECLARE
    NCOUNT NUMBER := 0;
BEGIN
    SELECT COUNT(1) INTO NCOUNT FROM DEPARTMENT;
    IF NCOUNT != 0 THEN
        --Delete from Lantusparam and Tusparam
        DELETE FROM LKTUPTACTPG WHERE TUSNOM = 'SECTEURGEST';
        DELETE FROM LANTUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'SECTEURGEST' ;
        DELETE FROM TUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'SECTEURGEST' ;
    END IF;
    COMMIT;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Deleted  from Lantusparam and Tusparam ') ;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Problem in Deleting from Lantusparam and Tusparam') ;
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
--CASNT-1873 END
-- Ticket ID TRUNK-2824 END

    DELETE FROM TUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'CSCWRKCATEGORY' AND TUPCODE = 'TESTWKCAT1';
    COMMIT;
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;

-- TRUNK-49 BEGIN
DECLARE
	NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
	SELECT COUNT(*)  INTO NCOUNT FROM TUSER WHERE TUSNOM = 'BSDTYPE';
	IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
		INSERT INTO TUSER
			(TUSNOM, TUSLONGUEUR
			) VALUES
			('BSDTYPE', 15
			) ;
		COMMIT;
	END IF;	
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('ERR TUSER BSDTYPE') ;
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
DECLARE
	NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
	SELECT COUNT(*)  INTO NCOUNT FROM LANTUSER WHERE TUSNOM = 'BSDTYPE' AND LANCODE = 'EN';
	IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
		INSERT INTO LANTUSER
			(TUSNOM, LANCODE, TUSLIBELLE
			) VALUES
			('BSDTYPE', 'EN', 'Unit transaction types'
			) ;
		COMMIT;
	END IF;	
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('ERR LANTUSER BSDTYPE EN') ;
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/
DECLARE
	NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
	SELECT COUNT(*)  INTO NCOUNT FROM LANTUSER WHERE TUSNOM = 'BSDTYPE' AND LANCODE = 'FR';
	IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
		INSERT INTO LANTUSER
			(TUSNOM, LANCODE, TUSLIBELLE
			) VALUES
			('BSDTYPE', 'FR', 'Lots : type de transaction'
			) ;
		COMMIT;
	END IF;	
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('ERR LANTUSER BSDTYPE FR') ;
END;
/
DECLARE
	NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
	SELECT COUNT(*)  INTO NCOUNT FROM TUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'BSDTYPE' AND TUPCODE = 'NEWFREE' ;
	IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
		INSERT INTO TUSPARAM
			(TUSNOM, TUPCODE, TUPFLAGORFI
			) VALUES
			('BSDTYPE', 'NEWFREE', 1
			) ;
		COMMIT;
	END IF;	
EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('ERR TUSPARAM BSDTYPE NEWFREE') ;
END;
/
DECLARE
	NCOUNT NUMBER;
BEGIN
	SELECT COUNT(*)  INTO NCOUNT FROM LANTUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'BSDTYPE' AND TUPCODE = 'NEWFREE' AND LANCODE = 'EN' ;
	IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
		INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM
			(TUSNOM, TUPCODE, LANCODE, TUPLIBELLE
			) VALUES
			('BSDTYPE', 'NEWFREE', 'EN', 'For sale'

    COMMIT;

    ROLLBACK;

-- BEGIN NLSCUAT-2076
BEGIN 
    UPDATE  LANTUSPARAM
    SET      TUPLIBELLE  = 'VALEUR/5'
    WHERE    TUSNOM = 'EVOATTESTDSP' AND  SUBSTR(TUPCODE,INSTR(TUPCODE,'/')+1,LENGTH(TUPCODE)-INSTR(TUPCODE,'/')) ='MONDV'; 
	COMMIT; 
	EXCEPTION
WHEN OTHERS THEN
	ROLLBACK;
	END;
/
-- END  NLSCUAT-2076

--KBCL-32 START
DECLARE
NCOUNT NUMBER;

CURSOR CPROCESS_FR IS
SELECT PRO.PROID AS CODEINTEGER, 
       PROLABEL  AS DISPLAYVALUE, 
       PROCODE   AS OTHERINFO 
FROM   PROCESS PRO, LANPROCESS LPA  
WHERE  LPA.PROID = PRO.PROID
AND    LANCODE = 'FR'
AND    PROTYPE = 'BATCHLAUNCH'
AND    PRO.PROID NOT IN (212,213,214);

CURSOR CPROCESS_EN IS
SELECT PRO.PROID AS CODEINTEGER, 
       PROLABEL  AS DISPLAYVALUE, 
       PROCODE   AS OTHERINFO 
FROM   PROCESS PRO, LANPROCESS LPA  
WHERE  LPA.PROID = PRO.PROID
AND    LANCODE = 'EN'
AND    PROTYPE = 'BATCHLAUNCH'
AND    PRO.PROID NOT IN (212,213,214);

BEGIN
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO NCOUNT FROM TUSER WHERE TUSNOM = 'BATCHWIZARD';

IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
 BEGIN
    INSERT INTO TUSER VALUES ('BATCHWIZARD', 15);
    COMMIT;
        EXCEPTION
         WHEN OTHERS THEN
         ROLLBACK;
    END;
END IF;


SELECT COUNT(*) INTO NCOUNT FROM TUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'BATCHWIZARD';

IF NCOUNT = 0 THEN
FOR CPROCESS_FR_REC IN CPROCESS_FR LOOP
    BEGIN
        INSERT INTO TUSPARAM VALUES ('BATCHWIZARD', CPROCESS_FR_REC.CODEINTEGER, NULL);
        INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM VALUES ('BATCHWIZARD', CPROCESS_FR_REC.CODEINTEGER, 'FR', CPROCESS_FR_REC.DISPLAYVALUE, CPROCESS_FR_REC.OTHERINFO );
        COMMIT;
        EXCEPTION
         WHEN OTHERS THEN
         ROLLBACK;
    END;
END LOOP;

FOR CPROCESS_EN_REC IN CPROCESS_EN LOOP
    BEGIN
        INSERT INTO TUSPARAM VALUES ('BATCHWIZARD', CPROCESS_EN_REC.CODEINTEGER, NULL);
        INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM VALUES ('BATCHWIZARD', CPROCESS_EN_REC.CODEINTEGER, 'FR', CPROCESS_EN_REC.DISPLAYVALUE, CPROCESS_EN_REC.OTHERINFO );
        COMMIT;
        EXCEPTION
         WHEN OTHERS THEN
         ROLLBACK;
    END;
END LOOP;
END IF;

END;
/

--KBCL-32 END

-- NLSCUAT-3843 start
DECLARE
	NCOUNT NUMBER:=0;
BEGIN
	SELECT COUNT(*) INTO NCOUNT FROM TUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'MOTTERRACTOT' AND TUPCODE IN ('NORMAL','VCTX','VDG');
	IF NCOUNT <> O THEN
		UPDATE TUSPARAM SET TUPFLAGORFI = 1 WHERE TUPCODE IN ('NORMAL','VCTX','VDG');
	END IF;
	COMMIT;
EXCEPTION
	WHEN OTHERS THEN
    ROLLBACK;
END;
/

-- TICKET_ROADTRK-33_ENDTICKET
-- VWTRK-788 START
DECLARE
nDtrid DATATRANSCODING.DTRID%TYPE;
nCount NUMBER;

BEGIN
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO nCount FROM DATATRANSCODING
WHERE DTRCODE = 'PWDHASHALGOMAP' ;

IF nCount = 0 THEN
    SELECT SEQ_DTRID.NEXTVAL INTO nDtrid FROM DUAL;
    
    BEGIN
    Insert into DATATRANSCODING (DTRID,DTRCODE,DTRTYPE,DTRTABLENAME,DTRFLAGMANDATORY,DTRMAXLENGTH,DTRDEFAULTVALUE,UGECODE,ACTID,TACCODE,TPGCODE) values (nDtrid,'PWDHASHALGOMAP','INTERNE',null,0,null,null,'_ORIG_',null,null,null);
    COMMIT;
    EXCEPTION
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
        ROLLBACK;
    END;
    
    BEGIN
    INSERT INTO DTRDETAIL values(nDtrid,'MD5', '2');
    COMMIT;
    EXCEPTION
       WHEN OTHERS THEN
           ROLLBACK;
    END;
	 BEGIN
    INSERT INTO DTRDETAIL values(nDtrid,'SHA-1', '3');
    COMMIT;
    EXCEPTION
       WHEN OTHERS THEN
           ROLLBACK;
    END;
	 BEGIN
    INSERT INTO DTRDETAIL values(nDtrid,'SHA-256', '4');
    COMMIT;
    EXCEPTION
       WHEN OTHERS THEN
           ROLLBACK;
    END;
   
END IF;
END;
/
--VWTRK-788 END

--ROADTRK-65 END
--TRUNK-3369 START
BEGIN
	DELETE FROM LANTUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'ACTBIDPARTTYPE' AND TRIM(TUPCODE) = 'USEDCAR';
	COMMIT;

	EXCEPTION
	WHEN OTHERS THEN
		DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Error : ' || SQLERRM );
	ROLLBACK;
END;
/
BEGIN
	DELETE FROM TUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'ACTBIDPARTTYPE' AND TRIM(TUPCODE) = 'USEDCAR';
	COMMIT;

	EXCEPTION
	WHEN OTHERS THEN
		DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Error : ' || SQLERRM );
	ROLLBACK;
END;
/
BEGIN
	UPDATE TUSPARAM SET TUPFLAGORFI = 1 WHERE TUSNOM = 'ACTBIDPARTTYPE' AND TUPCODE NOT IN ('USEDEALER');
	COMMIT;

	EXCEPTION
	WHEN OTHERS THEN
		DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Error : ' || SQLERRM );
	ROLLBACK;
END;
/
DECLARE
  nTUPCODE NUMBER;
BEGIN
  SELECT MAX(TUPCODE)+1 INTO nTUPCODE FROM TUSPARAM WHERE TUSNOM = 'DEPTYPE';

  INSERT INTO TUSPARAM VALUES ( 'DEPTYPE', nTUPCODE, 1);
  
  INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM VALUES ('DEPTYPE', nTUPCODE,'EN','Collection',NULL);
  INSERT INTO LANTUSPARAM VALUES ('DEPTYPE', nTUPCODE,'FR','Collection',NULL);
  
  COMMIT;
EXCEPTION
	WHEN OTHERS THEN
		DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Error : ' || SQLERRM );
	ROLLBACK;
END;
/
--TRUNK-3369 END

--VWTRK-824 START

BEGIN
	Insert into TUSER (TUSNOM,TUSLONGUEUR) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','15');		
	Insert into LANTUSER (TUSNOM,LANCODE,TUSLIBELLE) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','EN','Scale Mass Upload File Status');		
	Insert into LANTUSER (TUSNOM,LANCODE,TUSLIBELLE) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','FR','Statut du fichier de chargement de barmes');		
	Insert into TUSPARAM (TUSNOM,TUPCODE,TUPFLAGORFI) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','INI','1');	
	Insert into TUSPARAM (TUSNOM,TUPCODE,TUPFLAGORFI) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','VALIDATED','1');
	Insert into TUSPARAM (TUSNOM,TUPCODE,TUPFLAGORFI) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','CANCELLED','1');	
	Insert into LANTUSPARAM (TUSNOM,TUPCODE,LANCODE,TUPLIBELLE,TUPHELPTEXT) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','INI','EN','Initial',null);	
	Insert into LANTUSPARAM (TUSNOM,TUPCODE,LANCODE,TUPLIBELLE,TUPHELPTEXT) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','INI','FR','Initial',null);	
	Insert into LANTUSPARAM (TUSNOM,TUPCODE,LANCODE,TUPLIBELLE,TUPHELPTEXT) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','VALIDATED','EN','Validated',null);	
	Insert into LANTUSPARAM (TUSNOM,TUPCODE,LANCODE,TUPLIBELLE,TUPHELPTEXT) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','VALIDATED','FR','Valid',null);
	Insert into LANTUSPARAM (TUSNOM,TUPCODE,LANCODE,TUPLIBELLE,TUPHELPTEXT) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','CANCELLED','EN','Cancelled',null);	
	Insert into LANTUSPARAM (TUSNOM,TUPCODE,LANCODE,TUPLIBELLE,TUPHELPTEXT) values ('SCALEMUPSTATUS','CANCELLED','FR','Annul',null);

	COMMIT;

	EXCEPTION
	WHEN OTHERS THEN
		DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Error : ' || SQLERRM );
	ROLLBACK;
END;
